        <abstract>
            <p>Describes her compassion for all his sufferings and writes of her wish that his gratitude could be offered to heaven as well as to herself. To her, the only relief is to try to believe that suffering and illness are from God’s hand "to help us to exalt our minds &amp; to look forward with hope to a future state".</p>
        </abstract>
